
<title>| Register</title>
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:100,300,400,100italic,300italic,400italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
<body class="registration_body">
<div class="container-signup">

  <div class="banner">
    <img align= "center" id="Prodigy_Finance_Banner" src="../assets/prodigy_finance_logo_banner.png" height="85%" width="85%"> 
  </div>



<div class="main">
<div class="content col-xs-6">
<div class="registration-header">
<h3>Register</h3> 
<h5>    <p>Welcome to Prodigy Finance. By registering as an investor you will learn about the opportunities we provide to our investors, our partnering schools, and how your investment makes a difference in the lives of our students. <br />
         </h5>
</div>


<div class="registration-form">

<%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
<%= devise_error_messages! %>
     
      <h4>Personal Information</h4>

      <div><%= f.label :first_name,"First Name" %><br />
      <%= f.text_field :first_name %></div>

      <div><%= f.label :last_name,"Last Name" %><br />
      <%= f.text_field :last_name %></div>

      <div><%= f.label :email,"Email Address" %><br />
      <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true %></div>

      <div><%= f.label :password,"Password" %><br />
      <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off" %></div>

      <div><%= f.label :password_confirmation,"Confirm Password" %><br />
      <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off" %></div>

      <div><%= f.label :country_of_nationality,"Country of Nationality" %><br />
      <%= f.country_select :origin_country %></div>

      <div><%= f.label :country_of_residence,"Country of Residence" %><br />
      <%= f.country_select :resident_country  %></div>

      <h4>School Information</h4>

      <div ><%= f.label :school_id,"What school are you interested in investing in?" %><br>
        <%= f.collection_select(:school_id, School.all, :id, :name) %> 
      </div>


      <div ><%= f.label :alumnus_status,"Are you an alumnus of the school that you are interested in investing in?" %><br>
      <%= f.select :alumnus_status, ["Yes", "No"] %></div><br />  
      <div class="additional-q"><p>If you answered yes to the previous question, please answer the following question:</p></div> 
      <div> <%= f.label :grad_year, "What year did you graduate" %></div> 
      <div><%= f.select(:grad_year, (1950..Time.now.year)) %></div>  
     

      <div class= "button_row"> <%= f.submit "Register", class:"register_button" %></div>
      <% end %>
      <div class="inv-model">
      <h6>Since 2007, Prodigy Finance has been revolutionizing student finance. Our innovative model offers loans to international postgraduate students at leading universities and business schools. Through our community platform, alumni and other investors earn competitive returns, while students gain access to higher education they otherwise could not afford. We leverage the power of the alumni base to invest in the next class of MBA graduates. Over 150 nationalities are eligible for loans.</h6></div>
</div>
</div>


<div class="sidebar col-xs-6">
<div class="community">
<h2>The Prodigy Community</h2>
</div>
<div class="sidebar-image-wrapper">
<img align= "center" id="Prodigy_Finance" src="../assets/cranfield_mba_recipient.png"> 
</div>
<div class="description">
<h6>I chose Prodigy because of the close connection with Cranfield. I also loved the idea of prior MBA students being able to invest and get a return -- whilst giving students like me the chance to do something which I would not have been able to fund any other way. Post-MBA, I would now describe that as a virtuous circle!</h6>
</div>
<div class="investor_community">
<img align= "center" id="Prodigy_Finance" src="../assets/investor_community.png"> 
</div>
</div>

</div>
</div>

<%= render "footer" %>

</body>





